// StoveType Endpoints

### Get All Stove Types
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types

### Get Stove Type by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1

### Get Stove Type by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/99999

### Get Stove Type by ID (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/invalid

### Get Stove Types by Rarity (common)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/rarity/common

### Get Stove Types by Rarity (rare)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/rarity/rare

### Get Stove Types by Rarity (mythic)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/rarity/mythic

### Get Stove Types by Rarity (legendary)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/rarity/legendary

### Get Stove Types by Rarity (limited)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/rarity/limited

### Get Stove Types by Rarity (invalid)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/rarity/invalid

### Create Stove Type
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Test Stove",
    "imageUrl": "/images/stoves/test.png",
    "rarity": "common",
    "lootboxWeight": 50
}

### Create Stove Type (legendary)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Golden Dragon Stove",
    "imageUrl": "/images/stoves/golden-dragon.png",
    "rarity": "legendary",
    "lootboxWeight": 5
}

### Create Stove Type (duplicate name)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Standard Stove",
    "imageUrl": "/images/stoves/standard.png",
    "rarity": "common",
    "lootboxWeight": 100
}

### Create Stove Type (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Incomplete Stove"
}

### Create Stove Type (invalid rarity)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Invalid Rarity Stove",
    "imageUrl": "/images/stoves/invalid.png",
    "rarity": "super-rare",
    "lootboxWeight": 10
}

### Update Lootbox Weight
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1/weight
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "lootboxWeight": 75
}

### Update Lootbox Weight (invalid weight)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1/weight
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "lootboxWeight": -5
}

### Update Lootbox Weight (not found)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/99999/weight
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "lootboxWeight": 50
}

### Update Image URL
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1/image
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "imageUrl": "/images/stoves/updated.png"
}

### Update Image URL (missing URL)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1/image
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Delete Stove Type
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/2

### Delete Stove Type (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/99999

### Get Total Lootbox Weight
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/weight/total
